io.sphere.sdk.client.metrics

Class ObservedTotalDuration

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.sphere.sdk.models.Base
      • io.sphere.sdk.client.metrics.ObservedTotalDuration
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ObservedDuration

    public final class ObservedTotalDuration
extends Base
    The total amount of one execution of SimpleMetricsSphereClient.execute(SphereRequest) until the CompletionStage is completed.

    Due to multithreading issues (counter start and end is in different Threads) be aware that is measurement is not perfectly accurate.
